      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This Man became the Spirit then,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Whom we by faith receive."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s now the Man enthroned on high!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How can we not believe?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The living Word our spirit stirs,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we to God draw nigh,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spirit by the Spirit blessed"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Beneath an open sky."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Receive salvation’s helmet and"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Spirit as a sword,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Which Spirit is the Word of God,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By means of prayer’s accord."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "At every time, pray watchfully"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spirit, in God’s care,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Petitioning for all the saints,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus one another bear."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If God is for us, who indeed"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Can be against us still?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Who brings a charge ’gainst God’s elect?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ intercedes and will."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The love of God in Jesus Christ"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Encompasses all things,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So naught can separate us from"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His love, which sonship brings."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we take in the Word, we too"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Express God corporately,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Like-minded e’en like-souled become"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With God the Trinity."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Receive the Word by daily prayer"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In such a living way"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That darkness can’t avoid the light"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And death to life gives way!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Word is living, operative,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And sharper than a sword,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dividing soul from spirit by"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The light therein outpoured."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s presence and God’s speaking mark"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s Sabbath rest for us;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He speaks, we rest, and all is done."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His way is effortless."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our preparation as the Bride"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Depends upon the Word"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That sanctifies us inwardly,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Imbues us with the Lord!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God purposed in Himself to have"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A peerless counterpart,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Preparing us through words of life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Inscribed upon our heart."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Spirit calls us — overcome!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yea, hold fast what you have!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Take, eat the tree of life, be fed!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In Christ be strengthened, glad!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With hearts believing, ears to hear,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And eyes for Christ alone,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As one we cannot help but say,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Yes, come Lord, quickly come!”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    }
  ],
